name: Gift Certificate for ONE (1) Photo Session (only Seattle)
description:
Our photo session includes:

* One hour session
* Up to three outfit changes
* 15-20 web quality images
* 10 final digital high-resolution images 
* Online gallery on Zenfolio for one year
* $50 print credit 

The fine print:

*  Credit will be used once client selects the photos to be printed
*  Prints from Zenfolio are not included
*  Travelling costs (other states/abroad) are not included
*  Prices of sessions can change without notice

Sessions outside of Seattle Metro (only Washington) will have an additional mileage fee at the IRS rate of $0.50 per/mile.

name: Lapinas
description:
Photograph taken in Vilnius, Lithuania. 2009.

Lapinas is Lithuanian for "Dog". This photo features a stencil of a dog found on a wall during a stroll on the streets of Vilnius. Stencil wall art is widely spread in this stunning, awe-inspiring Baltic city. 

8x10 print.  Printed on Kodak Endura Professional Metallic Paper (C-Print).  Matted and framed in a Nielsen & Bainbridge Tuscany Collection 11x14 Silver Frame. Black framing available.

Shipping available only in the US. International shipping will be available soon.
